Class CarSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cccnj.FivePoints.Components.CarSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Actor

    public class CarSource
extends java.lang.Object
implements Actor
    CarSource is a Factory for class Car. It tracks how many cars have been created, and will create a new Car with a predestined Route.
